cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.IT

The paper discusses the use of automation and computer technology in medical image interpretation, specifically for vocal-fold imaging. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also discusses mathematical models of computation, which could fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) sub-categories. Finally, the paper discusses some of the exciting directions that automation will take in biomedical image analysis, which could fall under the information theory (cs.IT) sub-category.
